{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5835d70c88","title":"中共中央同意公安部关于严禁出动警察镇压革命学生运动的规定","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4a1f315765","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":22,"articleId":"5835d70c88","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"中共中央批示","id":"3a1b49d6e9","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"公安与法律","id":"53b954d860","type":"主题"},{"name":"资产阶级反动路线","id":"70f02a0dc7","type":"主题"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ac106db45d","type":"title","text":"中共中央同意公安部关于严禁出动警察镇压革命学生运动的规定","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5835d70c88","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f18d1405c4","type":"paragraph","text":"中央同意公安部的规定，希各级党委遵照执行。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5835d70c88","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b9bbf290d5","type":"paragraph","text":"严禁出动警察镇压革命学生运动","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5835d70c88","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ebc5a7681a","type":"paragraph","text":"主席、中央：","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5835d70c88","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"773aaacbc0","type":"paragraph","text":"最近，兰州、哈尔滨、西安、重庆等地，学生包围了省、市委住地。同时发生了两起人民警察镇压革命学生运动的严重事件。八月五日，兰州大学学生与铁路职工、铁路中学学生发生冲突，兰州市公安局出动上百名警察，在兰大门前实行戒严。八月二十日，陕西省铜川一中学生包围了市委，在场的公安派出所长杨万杰，竟擅自鸣枪示威。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5835d70c88","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5c002bd4d9","type":"paragraph","text":"镇压革命学生运动是一种违法犯罪行为，绝对不能允许。公安部六月十日曾通知各地，要全体公安干部、人民警察满腔热情地支持无产阶级文化大革命，支持革命师生闹革命，不准干涉学生的革命行动。但是少数地方没有认真执行。现再作如下规定：","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5835d70c88","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6669e30a98","type":"paragraph","text":"一、不准以任何借口，出动警察干涉、镇压革命学生运动。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5835d70c88","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"11bef72f94","type":"paragraph","text":"二、绝对不准向革命师生开枪，放空枪进行威吓也绝对不允许。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5835d70c88","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4dd97429ed","type":"paragraph","text":"三、重申除了确有证据的杀人、放火、防毒、破坏、盗窃国家机密等现行反革命分子，应当依法处理外，运动中一律不逮捕人。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5835d70c88","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"44cfce1a00","type":"paragraph","text":"四、重申警察一律不得进入学校。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5835d70c88","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6b79a53def","type":"paragraph","text":"五、警察只在街道维持秩序。遇有打架、斗殴，可以劝解。如革命学生打了警察，不准还手。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5835d70c88","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a0e3c0f9d5","type":"paragraph","text":"公  安  部","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5835d70c88","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"73fb20707c","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年八月二十二日","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5835d70c88","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}